Resource Profile: openIMIS Claim

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-claim Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISClaim

Defines a Claim for openIMIS which maps to a Claim.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: openIMIS CommunicationRequest and openIMIS Communication
  • Examples for this Profile: Claim/Claim001
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: openIMIS Capability Statement

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
